<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<mvt:item name="html_profile" />

<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<base href="&mvte:global:basehref;">

	<mvt:if expr="NOT ISNULL l.settings:page:title">
		<title>&mvt:page:title;</title>
	<mvt:else>
		<title>&mvt:page:name; | &mvt:store:name;</title>
	</mvt:if>

	<mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1">
		<mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" />
	<mvt:else>
		<mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" />
	</mvt:if>

	<mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" />
</head>

<body>
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />

	<main class="sd2-v2-help-center" data-v2-help-center>
		<div class="sd2-wrap">

			<header class="sd2-v2-hub-intro">
				<p class="sd2-eyebrow sd2-v2-hub-intro__eyebrow">Help Center</p>
				<h1 class="sd2-heading-lg sd2-v2-hub-intro__title">Help Center</h1>
				<p class="sd2-v2-hub-intro__body">
					Welcome to Sinister Diesel's Help Center! We're here to assist you with everything you need.
					Select the option that best fits your inquiry and our expert team will help you quickly resolve any issues.
				</p>
			</header>

			<div class="sd2-v2-help-notices">
				<div class="sd2-v2-vbanner">
					<span class="sd2-v2-vbanner__icon" aria-hidden="true">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5"/><path d="M12 7.5V12l3 2"/></svg>
					</span>
					<span class="sd2-v2-vbanner__text">Customer Service: Monday &ndash; Friday, 7:30 AM &ndash; 4:30 PM (PST)</span>
				</div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-vbanner sd2-v2-vbanner--notice">
					<span class="sd2-v2-vbanner__icon" aria-hidden="true">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6.5 4.5c0 8 5 13 13 13l1-3.2-4-1.6-1.5 1.6a10.5 10.5 0 0 1-5.3-5.3l1.6-1.5-1.6-4Z"/></svg>
					</span>
					<span class="sd2-v2-vbanner__text"><strong>Important:</strong> Most support is provided via phone from a 916 area code. Please check your call-blocking settings.</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="sd2-v2-help-grid">
				<a href="/help-sales-inquiry.html" class="sd2-v2-help-card">
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 16.5v.01M12 13.5c0-1.5 2-1.75 2-3.5a2 2 0 0 0-4 0"/></svg>
					</span>
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__body">
						<h2 class="sd2-v2-help-card__title">Sales Inquiry</h2>
						<p class="sd2-v2-help-card__desc">Questions about products, pricing, or need help choosing the right part?</p>
					</span>
				</a>

				<a href="/help-check-order-status.html" class="sd2-v2-help-card">
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3.5" y="7" width="17" height="13" rx="1.5"/><path d="M8 7V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 10.5 3h3A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 16 5.5V7M3.5 12h17"/></svg>
					</span>
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__body">
						<h2 class="sd2-v2-help-card__title">Order Tracking</h2>
						<p class="sd2-v2-help-card__desc">Track your order status, shipments, and get delivery updates.</p>
					</span>
				</a>

				<a href="/help-sinister-diesel-parts-tech-support.html" class="sd2-v2-help-card">
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 13a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/><path d="M4 13v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h1v-6H5a1 1 0 0 0-1 1Z"/><path d="M20 13v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1v-6h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1Z"/><path d="M12 19v1"/></svg>
					</span>
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__body">
						<h2 class="sd2-v2-help-card__title">Tech Support</h2>
						<p class="sd2-v2-help-card__desc">Get technical assistance with installation, troubleshooting, and part compatibility.</p>
					</span>
				</a>

				<a href="/help-warranty-inquiry.html" class="sd2-v2-help-card">
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3.5 19 6v6c0 4.2-2.9 7.4-7 8.5-4.1-1.1-7-4.3-7-8.5V6l7-2.5Z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
					</span>
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__body">
						<h2 class="sd2-v2-help-card__title">Warranty Inquiry</h2>
						<p class="sd2-v2-help-card__desc">Questions about warranty coverage, claims, or product registration?</p>
					</span>
				</a>

				<a href="/help-online-account-issues.html" class="sd2-v2-help-card">
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M9 9h6M9 12h6M9 15h3"/></svg>
					</span>
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__body">
						<h2 class="sd2-v2-help-card__title">Missing/Damaged Parts</h2>
						<p class="sd2-v2-help-card__desc">Report missing or damaged items and get quick replacements.</p>
					</span>
				</a>

				<a href="/help-shipping-protection-requests.html" class="sd2-v2-help-card">
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5 12 4l9 4.5v7L12 20l-9-4.5v-7Z"/><path d="M3 8.5 12 13l9-4.5M12 13v7"/></svg>
					</span>
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__body">
						<h2 class="sd2-v2-help-card__title">Shipping Claim</h2>
						<p class="sd2-v2-help-card__desc">File a claim for lost or stolen packages with shipping protection.</p>
					</span>
				</a>

				<a href="/help-returns-exchanges.html" class="sd2-v2-help-card">
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 12a8 8 0 0 1 13.5-5.5L20 8"/><path d="M20 4v4h-4"/><path d="M20 12a8 8 0 0 1-13.5 5.5L4 16"/><path d="M4 20v-4h4"/></svg>
					</span>
					<span class="sd2-v2-help-card__body">
						<h2 class="sd2-v2-help-card__title">Returns &amp; Exchanges</h2>
						<p class="sd2-v2-help-card__desc">Need to return or exchange a product? We'll guide you through the process.</p>
					</span>
				</a>
			</div>

		</div>
	</main>

	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" />
</body>
</html>
